{"tid":1533161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好不斷散播冇FC既標題資訊","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:18:17.000Z","uid":89775,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"057fa252e04b55a460919ef3683b874a5d8b3b00","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好成日未FC就大大隻標題打左個客觀結論出黎，咁樣唔係奸奸地咁贏，係不斷降低人地對我地一方所發放資訊既信心，令人覺得我地係散佈假資訊既一方，對我地根本冇益。<br />\n<br />\n我係狗警就不停散佈假消息，然後由你地煲一個禮拜先踢爆你地，令你地之後所散播既資訊都會受人質疑。<br />\n<br />\n單野比全球各大既media望住，黑警犯罪既證據根本係有哂證據，何必再用d不實既證據，圖同片去做佢地？<br />\n咁樣只會已來本身既支持者質疑我地尼方面既資訊。<br />\n<br />\n有片有圖有證據先好講結論！唔係開post之前記得加返個「未FC」或者「待查證」。<br />\n<br />\n黑警既資訊因爲講得大話多已經冇乜人信，但我地唔可以比人覺得我地都係發報緊假消息。"},{"pid":"ff8dea28febc65beefc89498e2712f30d484abbe","tid":1533161,"uid":66247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:27:35.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"6a2566383ce5f107ee161e805f50ad7db4077639","tid":1533161,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:27:54.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2fded992b866304d020a2266ab8602f03e7de5","tid":1533161,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:28:16.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"09e6fd02e278678808a595e25f530b742cb80683","tid":1533161,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"過左人權法再算"},{"pid":"23e7064e3943cb09a5db9b13eea7648a6127b977","tid":1533161,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係對家出緊招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8872135278298ddb85081ce4903208c5486c61d","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"假資訊會累到本身做緊文宣戰線既努力白廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好亂發佈"},{"pid":"9075afc6ce0515c14f1d865210fa9227513e64b6","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e7064e3943cb09a5db9b13eea7648a6127b977","tid":1533161,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係對家出緊招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"就係有，所以我地都唔好推，由佢沉<br />\n問題係我見熱門好多時有d未FC既post就大大隻字係標題打左個主觀結論出黎，仲要勁多人推。<br />\n<br />\n然後就炒哂車。<br />\n<br />\n都係果句，黑警依家唔識玩，佢識玩就煲你個幾禮拜先再踢爆你，等你地既資訊都變得唔可信。"},{"pid":"72c46fad8da9db0711e61e1f6f978af067218814","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6340241050d044096dc0fd9ca69bdc2b0576e7ec","tid":1533161,"uid":179120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:09:14.000Z","msg":"真，不得不推<br />\n求唔好成日開標題黨post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f961cceb5d498925b57d02b271660c1d1fa7c922","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c55c85492f0b9bfdbe3d2768a40e34f51e62b2","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f183d79979d703c713b7a7389ee8899f4fc54d3","tid":1533161,"uid":43422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c31c720b84e0f5ad19f118e0a4f51367b3cab6ca","tid":1533161,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"不如開個貼。。。集中舉報 fakes news, 標題五毛。。。等連仔做野"},{"pid":"021fe74fcf8afe35efec098a49358013ee5208d8","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909743e028590e7b55ee80d72babd20ef57208a9","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31c720b84e0f5ad19f118e0a4f51367b3cab6ca","tid":1533161,"uid":238745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"不如開個貼。。。集中舉報 fakes news, 標題五毛。。。等連仔做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"咁樣連仔會好唔得閒，佢為左搞黑客攻擊應該已經好忙。<br />\n各位巴打自律，<strong>見到標題黨唔好推</strong>，開post未fc既加返「未FC」或「待查」係前面。"},{"pid":"342785094066aa50339f47ac94e1d37fb85145ef","tid":1533161,"uid":89775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"或者自己開個標題寫好d既post<br />\n然後入標題黨既post用不推文回覆叫人轉去第個post討論"}]}